; |---------------------------------------------------------------------------|
; |                                                                           |
; | This packet will have the format of -                                     |
; |                                                                           |
; |     [RESET <type>,<version>]                                              |
; |                                                                           |
; | Where -                                                                   |
; |                                                                           |
; |     <type>     PICAXE type code is running on, eg "08M2"                  |
; |                                                                           |
; |     <version>  Version of the code running, eg "1.23"                     |
; |                                                                           |
